{"tid":1431797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港進入民主時代後第一件事 － 成立人民法庭審判黑警","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:18:26.000Z","uid":123264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c51835654e51a6f957b6dd81ee083f127389e28","tid":1431797,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"香港警察係不義政權下得到無限權力 隨意毆打示威者 公然侵犯婦權 破壞公眾秩序 <br />\n如果佢地唔係警察既身份 而係普通市民既身份 佢地做呢D野已經足夠坐成世監 <br />\n有左民主 抗爭勝利 係咪就等於可以放黑警一馬 等佢地用黑錢買番黎既物業同資產享福?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警犯過既罪行 絕對唔可以當無發生過</span></strong></span><br />\n當香港人民最終獲得勝利 無論係真普選定港獨 <br />\n我地必須成立人民法庭 對有紀錄既黑警罪行進行審判 咁樣先可以真正維護到法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d3c63f4459245e07f50604217dee566e980a26","tid":1431797,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598c5dc41f45e22ab5fcccc56fad660ca0f7e9e8","tid":1431797,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"883f539deccd5a1f971659fe13beb25c4074b3d0","tid":1431797,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d59fad6aaec3d54e4328226e7f43cf364714b6","tid":1431797,"uid":231909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:38:01.000Z","msg":"借個位,提提你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=aab03643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xp7KMz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxp7KMz5.png&h=1dddb453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">